Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.03,0:00:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.10,0:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第一節是魔法藥學課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個看起來很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我記得第一節課是聖魔法和治癒魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}米蘭達老師的課嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你準備和誰做室友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒定下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:01:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}貴安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.22,0:02:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.25,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭也是龍族的公主 叫我安就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.12,0:02:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:02:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前和你一起借的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我推薦的書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然還沒讀完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能了解瑪娜利亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}了解安的事情很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.48,0:03:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊的圖書館裡有許多不同的語言分支
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有好多的書庫 真想全部讀完
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說之前有找到關於龍族的書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭的國家是怎樣的一個地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和這裡不同 有好多大型的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 你為什麼選擇來這所學院呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 因為這裡是媽媽的母校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.71,0:04:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而我是人和龍族的混血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.26,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 原來你的母親也曾是這裡的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安學姐 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圖書館出大事了 快跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.90,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉古蕾婭 稍等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.76,0:04:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漢娜 你還行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很抱歉踩到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家後退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不愧是公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.97,0:05:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以封印它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能怪公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我下令封印書庫之主的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.07,0:06:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是漢娜她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.83,0:06:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甚至不能用自己的力量去控制局勢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我算什麼學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不配這個職位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問 有什麼我可以幫忙的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}非常感謝 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.88,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要事辦完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}封印後凍結了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}書庫之主發怒了 非常狂暴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一直在和大家處理後事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.93,0:09:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不會 一直在等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 你讓我等得有些久了…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安 餓了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.03,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說從早上開始還什麼都沒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們去吃點什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 甜的和辣的你選哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manaria Friends 第二話
